marketing: Shell Corena S3 RJ is a premium quality air compressor oil, formulated with synthetic technology base oils and designed to deliver high performance lubrication of rotary screw air compressors. It uses an advanced additive system to provide excellent protection and performance, particularly in Japanese compressor machinery where very low sludge, excellent thermal-oxidation stability and very high flash point are required.
